fields.Action: Stimulate the device to send an Inform – the easiest method may be to boot the device.
fields.Expected Result:
The device is able to send a correctly-formatted Inform message to the ACS.  Inform message elements are in the correct order, as specified in TR-069
	• DeviceId elements are all filled in – some devices sometimes leave some of the data out. The exception
	here is that ProductClass is allowed to be empty
	• The OUI in the DeviceId element is actually a properly-formatted OUI
	• Ensure that the events are correct and make sense. For instance, when a device is rebooted, “1 BOOT”
	must be included in the event list. If “1 BOOT” shows up in every Inform, even if the device has not
	rebooted, is an example of an incorrect event
	• Ensure that the number of events specified in the Event array definition actually matches the number of
	events in the array
	• Ensure that the number of parameters specified in the ParameterList array definition actually matches the
	number of parameters in the array
	• Ensure that the parameter list contains all of the forced Inform parameters (section 2.4.1 of TR-098
	Amendment 1 and/or section 3.5 of TR-106 Amendment 1)

	Following information are present in the Inform : 

	The following values have to be retrieved:
	+ xxxDevice.DeviceInfo.Manufacturer
	+ xxxDevice.DeviceInfo.ManufacturerOUI
	+ xxxDevice,DeviceInfo.ProductClass
	+ xxxDevice.DeviceInfo.SerialNumber
	+ xxxDevice.DeviceSummary
	+ xxxDevice.DeviceInfo.SpecVersion
	+ xxxDevice.DeviceInfo.ProvisioningCode
	+ xxxDevice.DeviceInfo.HardwareVersion
	+ xxxDevice.DeviceInfo.SoftwareVersion
	+ xxxDevice.WANDevice.{i}.WANConnectionDevice.{i}.WAN{***}Connection. {i}.ExternalIPAddress

	+xxxDevice.IP.Interface.{i}. Ipv6Address.[GUA].IPAddres s or Device.IP.Interface.{i}. Ipv6Address.[GUA_LAN].IPA ddress

fields.description:
The purpose of this test is to confirm that the device is able to send a proper Inform message.
[Precondition]

Please update this parameter : CONFIG_TR069_InformContent according to your platform.
